beer.beer_description:
Kalnapilis Grand Select - rich flavor, but light lager type beer.

Strong, long-lasting foam, and a subtle hop aroma gives nobility SELECT and BREWER'S GOLD combination. It is mixed, but the beer finishes cooking. It retained all the best features. 100% barley malt ensures obviously richer, amber color and a rich, ripe flavors.
